hat. I couldn't tell you the - I know work was part of it but I couldn't tell you the - real reason, because - that's a thing they never discussed with us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7556174 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5248227\charrsid6384043 Did your mother work at all after she was married?
