No. No. That's what I - I've always said that if you - let - if there was like - twenty coloured children - and 
twenty - black children - born today and they were put in a strange place - nothing - they would grow up you'd get none of that. But - this is passes from old - from - days of slavery this - started. Master this and master - oh - no.
\par 
