No. In fact I remember in one school I was a favourite. Old Miss Russell, a teacher from Penarch, and she used to bring, I always remember her, oh she was a nice teacher, she used to bring these - thin - ham sandwich 
- piece - sandwiches you know to school and there was always one for little me. Oh - so - no - teachers - they don't show no -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7556174 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5248227\charrsid6384043 What did your parents think of swearing?
