le party, invite our friends, yes. Yes. Mother'd make some jellies and - either make or buy some cakes and that and we'd invite our friends in and that were - sit down tea like and that. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7556174 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5248227\charrsid6384043 Would you have any presents?
