rdly. Of course if there was some friends of mother's friends in the house and dad come in he'd join in the conversation and all that but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7556174 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5248227\charrsid6384043 Your mother had lots of friends didn't she?
