 generally when I go in the house they might be sat round talking and all that kind of thing - and then as I say - I wasn't allowed to - to join in no }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6512867\charrsid6384043 conversa}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5248227\charrsid6384043 tions. No.
